		<div>My first world war was not suprisingly in my first game. I had just finished conquering Persia, who was on a contient with the Babylonians. I owned the two islansds near my home contient (which I had cleansed of the American and Iroqoius filth- playing Aztecs here) and was mobilizing for a war against Babylon, who was roughly a tech or two behind me the entire game. I just got in industrial and was producing cavalry.<br />
